@page "/download"

<PageTitle>Download Mobile App</PageTitle>

<div class="container py-4">
    <h1>Download the LoyaltyCRM Mobile App</h1>
    <p>
        Download the latest Android APK for the LoyaltyCRM Mobile App.
        Place the signed APK file at <code>wwwroot/downloads/LoyaltyCRM.MobileApp.apk</code> in the WebApp project,
        then rebuild/publish the WebApp so the new version is served.
    </p>
    <div class="mb-3">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="downloads/LoyaltyCRM.MobileApp.apk" download>
            Download APK
        </a>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p><strong>Android installation notes:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Use an Android tablet and enable installation from unknown sources if needed.</li>
            <li>Open the downloaded APK to install the app.</li>
            <li>If the file is missing, add the APK to <code>wwwroot/downloads</code> and republish the web app.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
